{"tid":1420832,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港澳辦即將舉行吹風會","createTime":"2019-08-06T05:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T06:58:59.000Z","uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"44289c971d95c03fec762b51faac7219bd37d201","tid":1420832,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:57:20.000Z","msg":"中國國務院新聞辦公室昨天通知各別媒體，6日下午2時30分舉行吹風會，由國務院港澳事務辦公室新聞發言人楊光、徐露穎「介紹對香港當前局勢的看法，並答記者問」。<br />\n<br />\n這場吹風會並未邀請台灣媒體，也僅有少數港媒能進入會場，直到今天上午11時許，中國國務院台灣事務辦公室才通知駐京台媒，吹風會「場地有限」，只有受邀的港澳及外國媒體記者能入場，國新辦另外設置現場實況轉播室，持有國新辦發佈會採訪證的台灣記者，可以到觀看室收看轉播。<br />\n<br />\n中國國新辦今天全天共舉行3場記者會，許多香港與台灣媒體早在上午10時，便已抵達現場，希望能順利占到下午的採訪位置。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idNuHtK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidNuHtK.jpg&h=bb8de510&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"125756c6011fb94778d9cfad2acfc7fd8c9f5fd8","tid":1420832,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:58:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201908060112.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Facn%2F201908060112.aspx&d=NNqT6wnuCkALqD5scUUSnBjE8xiivR5AeW87zNloLfY%3D&h=f9077bd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/acn/201908060112.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"ad8817c912a16826658b9973e64d5e7216c38ce6","tid":1420832,"uid":997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:59:18.000Z","msg":"解放軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />解放軍 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0453a93f67046c7f0f4ffe01655a7d2660ad562b","tid":1420832,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T05:59:39.000Z","msg":"國務院港澳辦6日將召開記者會 南早：傳有「新消息宣布」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1413617/page/9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1413617/page/9</a>"},{"pid":"bb7a98c0511f5cff50cd233c04add692158ea9cd","tid":142083